{"tid":1551550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日無得出中環 有去嘅手足你地加油","createTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:10:23.000Z","uid":279880,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35e9550e9d7c7bf20551cff6bf83801f2c70aad9","tid":1551550,"uid":279880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n（和理非）<br />\n<br />\n本來今日真係好想去，但由於係星期日，家母係屋企望住，唔比我去😢<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講句，各位手足加油，我唔係現場，我只可以精神上支找你地。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.全屋黃絲，但家母覺得popo信唔過，有不反對通知書都唔準去。<br />\n<br />\nP.P.S.光復香港 時代革命🇭🇰"},{"pid":"88ae82afacd8659849aea627b9f7fdf3d5fc3c2e","tid":1551550,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"今日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱fuck the popo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱毅進仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱今天我 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係唱The Star-Spangled Banner</span>🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一定一定要係國際媒體面前一齊全民大合唱啊<br />\n點都要唱到第一段啊！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<del>因為全首太長</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\nOh, say can you see by the dawn's early light<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars thru the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there.<br />\nOh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對記者資料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂][行動] 9月8點應對外國記者+3首歌歌詞+資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551469\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7fae3ad1ae9c3f4a0247b09abe304ab3fa8ef55c","tid":1551550,"uid":74929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16DxAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16DxAR.jpg&h=6b663e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1mTkZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1mTkZ7.jpg&h=106f1e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F08%2F121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg&h=0ace8822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gvdmuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gvdmuh.jpg&h=88cf1465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>美國國歌唔同大陸國歌唔需要一定跟著唱 大部份場合只有一個領唱者</ins> <br />\n<br />\n唔識唱嘅話單手放心口就得<br />\n唔想放喺心口嘅話面向國旗都可<br />\n<br />\n記得除帽 口罩要帶保護返自己<br />\n美國佬好隨和其實着咩都冇所謂<br />\n<ins>最緊要有人到有心最重要</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>今日大家美國領事館見</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n緊急9月8號 weconnect美國重要日子 注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551454\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"24a814be642b2ca447e99c75440d15eecffaf1b9","tid":1551550,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"出啦"},{"pid":"d3e774a4482a3fb4ef199872f59e9fea6061dc92","tid":1551550,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"差你一個，出黎啦"},{"pid":"7fbe502a566dad535d0eddb883b56e1ef902352d","tid":1551550,"uid":190895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:09:24.000Z","msg":"叫埋屋企人一齊去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc64acd35bbb27ca6d2624534324ba9df81da10","tid":1551550,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35e9550e9d7c7bf20551cff6bf83801f2c70aad9","tid":1551550,"uid":279880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n（和理非）<br />\n<br />\n本來今日真係好想去，但由於係星期日，家母係屋企望住，唔比我去😢<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講句，各位手足加油，我唔係現場，我只可以精神上支找你地。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.全屋黃絲，但家母覺得popo信唔過，有不反對通知書都唔準去。<br />\n<br />\nP.P.S.光復香港 時代革命🇭🇰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"咁係咪即係所有遊行示威活動都唔出席得"},{"pid":"ee3a34f19aba3f6b0aac0b124a5d0fff1387c98a","tid":1551550,"uid":125724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"我阿媽係藍，我都去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c92da063bacd2efdd32e502c9587709838a002","tid":1551550,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">We Will Protect You</span>"}]}